Package: paneltools
Title: Panel Data DiD Visualisation Tools
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("First", "Last", email = "simfavot99@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Helper functions for visualising Difference-in-Differences estimates
    from panel data, with a focus on the did_multiplegt_stat estimators
    (AOSS, WAOSS, IV-WAOSS) introduced by de Chaisemartin et al. (2022).
